nodes.text: During the Clone Wars, the Confederacy of Independent Systems dispatched a blockade of Felucia and large amount of ground forces. These forces kept the Galactic Republic at bay from the planet that was the headquarters of the Commerce Guild, as well as control of the Perlemian Trade Route. The blockade resulted in the First Battle of Felucia, which led to a Confederacy victory. The naval complement of the blockade consisted of at least four Munificent-class frigates, one of which was destroyed.
